{
  "texts": [
    "This setup enables efficient data processing, reduces latency, and optimizes resource usage.",
    "Leveraging microservices-based frameworks and advanced resource allocation algorithms further ensures smooth operation, even as system demands grow (Khaleel et al., 2024).",
    "Maintaining and updating NLP models in real-world settings pose additional difficulties, particularly in environments with diverse hardware and software ecosystems.",
    "The heterogeneity of devices can lead to inconsistencies and increase vulnerabilities, complicating efforts to ensure that all components stay synchronized and up-to-date (Gill et al., 2024).",
    "Solution: Containerization and orchestration tools, such as Docker and Kubernetes, can manage these challenges by isolating services and automating updates across environments."
  ]
}